    <item>
      <title>中国公民赞扬 DeepSeek 的成就，对美国芯片限制感到自豪</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-28/chinese-citizens-hail-deepseek-s-feat-gloat-about-us-chip-curbs</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着 DeepSeek 更廉价的人工智能模式在全球产生冲击，很多中国人开始接受这家本土创业公司，认为它是一项有可能改写历史的国家级突破。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-28/chinese-citizens-hail-deepseek-s-feat-gloat-about-us-chip-curbs</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 28 Jan 2025 05:58:04 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>SAP Cloud 增长超出 Pivot to AI 工具的销售预期</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-28/sap-cloud-growth-tops-estimates-as-clients-seek-ai-capabilities</link>
      <description><![CDATA[SAP SE 公布的第四季度云计算销售额略高于分析师预期，这家欧洲最大的科技公司凭借新的人工智能功能赢得了客户。该公司还任命了一批新高管，并表示计划简化其战略。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-28/sap-cloud-growth-tops-estimates-as-clients-seek-ai-capabilities</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 28 Jan 2025 05:05:34 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>本田瞄准全球摩托车市场 50% 的份额</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-28/honda-sets-its-sights-on-50-share-of-world-s-motorcycle-market</link>
      <description><![CDATA[本田摩托车公司希望占领全球摩托车市场的一半份额，因为到 2030 年，整个行业的汽油和电动两轮车销量预计将达到每年 6000 万辆。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-28/honda-sets-its-sights-on-50-share-of-world-s-motorcycle-market</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 28 Jan 2025 04:30:29 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
